snippet.title: Stone Cage (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Stone Cage is 'horror' game inspired by covetous(pixel art,tone and gameplay) but is its own thing.It will be short about 5 minutes (so you won't waste much time trying it out),music is atmospheric with 8 bit effects.Game is about interesting and tense story so it would be balefully to spoil it for you...so what are you waiting for?

if you want to support me follow this game and like it on itch.io and game jolt and sub...

Itch.io:https://gamejolt.com/games/Stone_Cage/441687

game jolt:https://andrya.itch.io/stone-cage
